Package: metabom8
Type: Package
Title: A High-Performance R Package for Metabolomics Modeling and Analysis
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Torben",
            family = "Kimhofer",
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
            email = "tkimhofer@gmail.com",
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7158-9930"))
Description: Tools for 1D NMR metabolomics workflows, including import and 
              preprocessing of Bruker data, multivariate modeling (PCA, OPLS), metabolite 
              identification, and visualization with ggplot2 and plotly. Performance-critical 
              routines are implemented in C++ and use the Armadillo and Eigen linear algebra 
              libraries to improve runtime.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
